nt strain of the OPD noise to that of TQ, and find that the OPD\nnoises for the TDI combinations can be neglected in the most sensitive\nfrequency range of TQ.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 21 Feb 2021 10:06:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Apr 2021 09:24:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-30"}
